snippet.title: Why Top Movie Studios Won’t Sign Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Why Top Movie Studios Won’t Sign Amber Heard?

As of right now, we are very unsure of Amber Heard’s professional acting career in Hollywood, but what we do currently know is that because she is fighting major court cases right now with her ex-husband, Johnny Depp The case is one that is revealing not so good things about her and her reputation. From this several fans have expressed their own personal desires to have her removed from role, Mira, in Aquaman 2. 

Because of all of this one can clearly see that she has gotten herself in a lot of trouble and is now currently looking to make a jump into another major movie franchise, if that is even possible. Now there is quite a bit that is taking place with Amber Heard's career.
